summary: So I have posted about this before but I will do it once more. I have these two Dan and Phil photos that I got signed when I was...
body:
So I have posted about this before but I will do it once more. I have these two Dan and Phil photos that I got signed when I was at TATINOF that I don’t really want anymore. The picture to the left is signed by both Dan and Phil while the one to the right only has Phil’s.

I have had a fall out with them and just doesn’t feel the same joy towards them as I did when I met them and want someone that would appreciate them more to have them. I also have a TATINOF poster and a TATINOF badge that I am also willing to give away if anyone would want them. OH and some Interactive Introvert stuff (a badge and a bracelet), otherwise I will just throw it all away.
